<plot>Francine (Regine Velasquez) is starting to feel the toll of stardom. Her popularity and hectic schedule hinders her from enjoying a normal life. Meanwhile, because he felt cheated of his prize in a "Date with a Star" promo where he supposedly won a date with her, Gimo (Robin Padilla) kidnaps Francine. Being the candid person that he is, Gimo allows the singing sensation to take pleasure in living life's simple pleasures - which Francine later realizes she's been missing. But is Francine willing to give up her career? Not just to go back to ordinary life but also to live it with the special man who addresses her complexities.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?284433</url></doc>
